<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-11-01T19:10:24-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-11-01T19:10:24-04:00</published><updated> 2024-11-01T19:10:24-04:00</updated><title>现代可爱的 Inster EV 不需要很快</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浅绿色小车&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6mayMmxqLeMfA4euiwqR8Zz73Ys=/0x0:1499x999/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/73694930/Image_4.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这适合大多数停车位。&lt;/em>; |图片：现代&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OqcNTF&quot;>;现代小型电动 SUV 的评论&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.expressandstar.com/news/motors/reviews/2024 /11/01/first-drive-hyundais-inster-delivers-a-premium-experience-in-a-compact-package/&quot;>;是&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.topgear.com /car-reviews/hyundai/inster&quot;>;涓滴&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/cars/electric-vehicles/hyundai-inster-review-electric-car-b2638781。 html&quot;>;in&lt;/a>;，很明显，Inster 是一种令人愉快的城市出行方式——尽管与其他类似尺寸的电动汽车相比，它缺乏速度。根据 &lt;a href=&quot; 的说法，长程版 Inster 的最高时速约为 93 英里/小时（或 150 公里/小时），并且可在 10.6 秒内从零加速到 62 英里/小时（100 公里/小时）。 https://www.hyundai.com/worldwide/en/newsroom/detail/0000000860&quot;>;现代汽车今天发布的规格&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;X0atai&quot;>;现代汽车还透露了有关 Inster 的更多细节价格，欧洲评论家表示，与同类竞争产品相比，它的售价为 23,495 英镑（约合 25,477 美元）。然而，在美国，这是我们只能梦想的价格，因为我们最实惠的选择包括 35,000 美元 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/12/24070558/gm-chevy-equinox -ev-price-range-trim-model-date&quot;>;雪佛兰 Equinox EV&lt;/a>; 或希望特斯拉...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/11/1/24285787/hyundai-inster-ev-small-compact-ev-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24285787/hyundai-inster-ev-small-compact-ev-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24285787/hyundai-inster-ev-small-compact-ev-specs</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-01T19:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-11-01T19:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 《堡垒之夜》以 Snoop Dogg 和 Ice Spice 音乐会拉开混音第 2 季的序幕</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《堡垒之夜》中的史努比狗狗。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ELroXwaVCXF2_ZFL4KixPt69ZN4=/291x0:1716x950/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73694905/FNBR_CH2Remix_Screenshot_Still001_Lo​​go_192 0x1080.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Epic Games&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zf7JjL&quot;>;&lt;em>;Fortnite&lt;/em>; 时钟再次倒转。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24285464/fortnite-remix-the-prelude-event-how-to-watch&quot;>;经过一番调侃&lt;/a>;， Epic 即将开启大逃杀游戏的新时代，名为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fortnite.com/news/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-run-it-back-with-snoop- eminem-ice-spice-and-juice-wrld-in-battle-royale&quot;>;混音：第 2 章&lt;/a>; - 它不仅回顾了过去，而且以一种雄心勃勃的新方式整合了音乐。&lt;/p >; &lt;p id=&quot;s2lnkI&quot;>;混音季推出之前举办了一场音乐活动，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/2/23978521/fortnite-the-big -bang-eminem-chapter-5&quot;>;类似于为《堡垒之夜》开启新时代的阿姆演唱会&lt;/a>;。这一次，Snoop Dogg 和 Ice Spice 登上了舞台——无论是在游戏中还是在纽约时代广场的现实生活中——一旦赛季开始，音乐方面将更进一步。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Epic Games&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YDaM0e&quot;>;顾名思义，新的迷你赛季带回了许多游戏第二个的角色、游戏元素和地点...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24283508/fortnite-remix-chapter -2-concert-snoop-dogg-ice-spice&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24283508/fortnite-remix-chapter-2-concert-snoop-dogg-ice-spice" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24283508/fortnite-remix-chapter-2-concert-snoop-dogg-ice-spice</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-01T18:42:31-04:00</published><updated> 2024-11-01T18:42:31-04:00</updated><title> Bose 在黑色星期五之前推出耳机高达 40% 的折扣</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/5Q6wFkqe8ZjqwGsmleA80ZA9lX8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73694878/DSCF3714.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;凭借出色的 ANC，QuietComfort Ultra 耳机成为我们乘坐飞机时的第一选择。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Tag9iV&quot;>;嗯，早期的黑色星期五优惠不到一天就开始了。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/b/?node=122248329011&amp;amp;ref_=nav_cs_events_holi_2024_desktop&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://bestbuy.7tiv.net/c/ 482924/614286/10014?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fclp%2Fsale-page%2Fpcmcat185700050011.c%3Fid%3Dpcmcat185700050011&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 noopener&quot;目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://lowes.sjv.io/c/482924/897039/12374?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowes.com%2Fpl %2FBlack-friday-buildup%2F2311517799048&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Lowe&#39;s&lt;/a>; 和许多其他主要零售商已正式开始预期的假日促销活动年度购物活动的一部分，尽管很少有人提供像 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tkqlhce.com/click-8836598-11556694?sid=vergeroundupdeals110124&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww 这样大的折扣.bose.com%2Fc%2Fholiday-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose&lt;/a>;。在有限的时间内，您可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort-Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B0CCZ1L489? tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/2193452/9383?subId1= vergeroundupdeals110124&amp;amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FBose-QuietComfort-Ultra-Wireless-Noise-Cancelling-Bl